      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. This specimen features the S54B32 inline-six power plant, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS to achieve exceptional volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain is configured with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque to a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Mechanical integrity is absolute: the rod bearings have been replaced as a preventative measure, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with structural plates to ensure chassis rigidity. Suspension remains true to factory kinematics with fresh bushings and Sachs dampers. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or delamination. This is a turn-key collector piece for the purist demanding peak mechanical performance.",
